"{\"uid\": \"horseandhound.co.uk-features-olympic-eventing-dressage-test-755665\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Event riders competing at theParis Olympicswill be riding anOlympic eventingdressage test that was first introduced at theTokyo Olympicsin 2021.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Event riders\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 12}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympicswill\", \"from\": 26, \"to\": 47}, {\"ngram\": \"anOlympic eventingdressage test\", \"from\": 58, \"to\": 89}, {\"ngram\": \"theTokyo Olympicsin\", \"from\": 119, \"to\": 138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The shortened dressage test, which lasts just under 4mins, was designed to make the phase more spectator-friendly with movements coming up more quickly.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The shortened dressage test\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 173}, {\"ngram\": \"the phase\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"movements\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This means it is more intense for both horse and rider.\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both horse\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 343}, {\"ngram\": \"rider\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With fewer movements and less time to reorganise between them, it will be harder to score top marks and there are fewer opportunities to demonstrate the horse's talent and training to the judges.\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fewer movements\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 378}, {\"ngram\": \"less time\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 392}, {\"ngram\": \"top marks\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 457}, {\"ngram\": \"fewer opportunities\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 491}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse's talent\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The test includes movements not previously seen in eventing dressage including the canter zig-zag (canter half-pass in one direction, flying change, then canter half pass in the other direction, and a flying change) and walk to counter canter.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 797, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The test\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"movements\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"dressage\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"the canter zig\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"zag\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"canter\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"one direction\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 686}, {\"ngram\": \"flying change\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"the other direction\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"counter canter\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Top international dressage judge Stephen Clarke, says the Olympic eventing dressage test is \\\"very difficult, with no let-ups\\\".\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Top international dressage judge Stephen Clarke\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic eventing dressage test\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"no let-ups\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The counter canter strike off, which is quickly followed by two flying changes on a straight line across the diagonal is particularly challenging,\\\" says Stephen.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The counter canter strike\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"two flying changes\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1008}, {\"ngram\": \"a straight line\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"the diagonal\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"Stephen\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If combinations make a mistake in that movement, it will be very hard for them to recover.\\\"\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"combinations\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"that movement\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephen was on hand atRoyal Windsor Horse Showwhen the British squad ran through the test in public for the first time ahead of flying to Tokyo in 2021.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999956697668572, \"rank\": 2.1937239049670183e-06, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1324, \"end\": 1329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9482532969007232, \"rank\": 0.054502454586880744, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stephen\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"hand atRoyal\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"Windsor Horse Showwhen\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"the test\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"public\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It takes a very well-trained horse to do it well - those who have performed the test proved that if a horse is not on its rider's aids, they will lose marks - there is no room for error,\\\" says Stephen.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very well-trained horse\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"the test\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"a horse\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"its rider's aids\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"marks\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"no room\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"error\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"Stephen\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Five-star event rider and British eventing team regular,Kitty King, who was shortlisted for these Games and has ridden through the test in training, says: \\\"It's a very fast and furious test in that everything comes up very, very quickly.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1570, \"end\": 1586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Eventing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British eventing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Eventing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Eventing\"}, {\"begin\": 1600, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kitty_King\", \"score\": 0.9999969113930496, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kitty King\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kitty_King\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kitty_King\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Five-star event rider\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1647}, {\"ngram\": \"the test\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"a very fast and furious test\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is the same amount of movements as a normal five-star test, but squeezed into a lot less time.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same amount\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"movements\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1819}, {\"ngram\": \"a normal five-star test\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1846}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot less time\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you make one mistake, it's really hard to recover, and I think the trickiest thing is that horses and riders do not have the time to recover from a mistake before the next movement comes up.\\\"\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 2079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one mistake\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"the trickiest thing\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"riders\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"the next movement\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the canter half-pass zig-zag, Kitty says: \\\"You have to be very prepared - you want to finish the half-pass a little early so you have a couple of straight strides through your change.\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the canter\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"zag\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"Kitty\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"straight strides\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"your change\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then you need to get back across in time to have your horse straight and get your other change in before you run out of room at the end of the arena.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"your horse\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2327}, {\"ngram\": \"your other change\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"room\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2392}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have to be incredibly accurate to give the horse time, rather than rushing across in one direction and then flying back the other way.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the horse time\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"one direction\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's trying to make it feel like you have got time to prepare the horse and to do good straight changes and then get into the half-pass nicely.\\\"\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2630}, {\"ngram\": \"good straight changes\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kitty also highlighted the walk to counter canter as being a challenge.\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kitty\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"the walk\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2736}, {\"ngram\": \"canter\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2754}, {\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Going from walk straight into counter-canter is not a difficult movement, but the event horses normally walk and pick up true canter, and so it would be easy for horses to anticipate what they normally do,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"counter\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"canter\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2823}, {\"ngram\": \"a difficult movement\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2851}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2866}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"true canter\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2911}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As a rider you have to be very clear with your aids and what you are actually asking so the horse does not second guess you.\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rider\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3007}, {\"ngram\": \"your aids\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's much more like a pure dressage test.\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pure dressage test\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Also the first centre line requires you to go from canter to trot, whereas horses at this level are used to going from canter to halt, so through trying too hard, they might drop behind their riders.\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3365, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first centre line\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3192}, {\"ngram\": \"canter\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3223}, {\"ngram\": \"trot\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3231}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3247}, {\"ngram\": \"this level\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3261}, {\"ngram\": \"canter\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3291}, {\"ngram\": \"their riders\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I trained my horses in this new movement so that they did not try to anticipate the halt.\\\"\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my horses\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3385}, {\"ngram\": \"this new movement\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3406}, {\"ngram\": \"the halt\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dressage phase of the Olympic eventing competition is taking place on one day in Paris, with all 65 competitors taking part in the first phase on Saturday 27 July.\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3543, \"end\": 3548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998065873301, \"rank\": 1.9341262439946172e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"]